            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Domin<supplied reason="lost">o nostro</supplied> <lb n="2"/>Gratiano Pio <supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>Fel</abbr><ex>ici</ex></expan></supplied> <lb n="3"/>victori ac tri<supplied reason="lost">um</supplied><lb break="no" n="4"/>fatori semper A<supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>ug</abbr><ex>usto</ex></expan></supplied> <lb n="5"/>Leptitani de<supplied reason="lost">voti</supplied> <lb n="6"/>numini mai<supplied reason="lost">esta</supplied><lb break="no" n="7"/>tique eius
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>(B): AE 1929: Z. 1: D]omino [n(ostro)], Z. 2: Gratiano im[p(eratori)], Z. 3-4: tri[um]/fatori. The inscription is carved over an erased earlier text.</p>
            </div>
